csw.time.core.models

Interface TMTTime

  • All Superinterfaces:
    scala.Equals, scala.Product, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TAITime, UTCTime

    public interface TMTTime
extends scala.Product, scala.Serializable
    Represents an instantaneous point in time. Its a wrapper around Instant and provides nanosecond precision. Supports 2 timescales: - UTCTime for Coordinated Universal Time (UTC) and - TAITime for International Atomic Time (TAI)
